== Industry
*Nanjing Xiuming Fund Private Limited Company*, 2025.9-2025.12
Quantitative Research Position

- Built a systematic performance attribution framework integrating GRAP-based long–short strategies with multi-period Brinson and Carino-linked Barra factor models.
- Delivered end-to-end return decomposition across industry allocation, stock selection, and enabling transparent and interpretable alpha attribution.
- Built a scalable attribution engine for continuous monitoring of factor exposures and strategy performance drivers.
- Enhanced decision-making efficiency in portfolio optimization and risk control through rigorous quantitative attribution and diagnostics.


*Shenzhen Power Supply Bureau*, 2025.3–2025.7
Electric Power Research Institute

- Participated in research on power system stability and wideband oscillation analysis, assisting in the theoretical study and algorithm implementation for related patent work.
- Contributed to the analysis of oscillation component extraction methods under complex operating conditions and supported preliminary engineering validation.
- Assisted in the evaluation process of national standards under SAC/TC1 and contributed to supporting work for distribution network risk assessment guidelines.
- Supported literature review and technical analysis on medium-voltage distribution network broadband impedance and related topics.

*China Light Industry Changsha Engineering Co., Ltd.*, 2022.7–2022.8
Energy and Environmental Protection Department

- Participated in energy system planning tasks for industrial parks and manufacturing enterprises, assisting in feasibility analysis of distributed photovoltaic integration and grid expansion projects.
- Assisted in technical drawing review and basic validation work to support engineering design processes.
- Supported data collection and preliminary analysis of industrial energy demand for equipment selection and energy efficiency comparison.
- Participated in research on the implementation of energy policies in industrial energy conservation and emission reduction.